      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7487,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "ёкай",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mikoshi Chiyo was a crimson oni.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1090730713764694732.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Катаклизм в Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "During the Cataclysm 500 years ago, Chiyo was once devoured whole by a beast from beyond this world, with the body of a tiger and the tail of a serpent, until she tore the creature apart from within. Although she escaped the belly of the beast alive, this battle never left her. She saw the memories of her fallen comrades everywhere, slaughtered one after another until she could no longer distinguish dream from reality. The nightmare twisted every joy in her life — her subordinates, family, and friends — into enemies in need of destruction.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7470,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Вельзевул",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ei and Chiyo were friends but Ei was forced to use the Musou no Hitotachi when Chiyo attacked her, trapped in the battlefield of her mind by the Nightmare.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7498,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Кицунэ Сайгу",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kitsune Saiguu and Chiyo were friends. Together they played divine music before the throne, and the kitsune applauded the oni's sword dance. Thinking of Chiyo's unrivaled beauty, Kitsune Saiguu couldn't help but want to hide her appearance behind a mask.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4907,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/20/237301566/08ad31cb2d00748c8a122eb1c2562ff8_3486406714046377869.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Макото",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7499,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Сасаюри",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mikoshi Chiyo's friends",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mikoshi Michihiro",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Chiyo's son, who fled to Konda Village after his mother's attack on the Shogun and renounced his name, becoming Iwakura Michihiro, also known as Douin. He founded the Iwakura Arts.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Mikoshi Nagamasa",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Chiyo's adopted son, who joined the Shogunate after his mother's attack on the Shogun to regain his clan's former trust. When his yoriki Katsuragi was connected with but a single trace of misconduct, he had him executed without mercy.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Kinkaku",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Ginkaku",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tetsunosuke",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Three bake-danuki who found a piece of Chiyo's horn that was cut off by Raiden. The Nightmare from the horn spread to the youkai, causing them to see everyone as an enemy.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3450,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/26/237301566/8e15d77396d6a387b146a2cc7a65d735_2997003665821390978.png",
